{"tid":695072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓國TL韓梓亮】 G-Dragon軍中受傷入院做手術","createTime":"2018-06-09T02:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:25.000Z","uid":152123,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"010a22ed60dda47963bad54a61a71e2a7bea2f8c","tid":695072,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180517/s00009/4551f88cf8df66b214a73f4207c82e1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180517%2Fs00009%2F4551f88cf8df66b214a73f4207c82e1a.jpg&h=077e4919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人稱韓國TL韓梓亮的韓國男團BigBang隊長G-Dragon（GD）今年2月入伍，早前完成新兵訓練，正以現役兵身分服兵役。據韓媒今日報道，GD上月中透過軍方醫院接受治療，並轉介至首爾大學醫院，其後醫生建議他接受右腳腳踝手術，據報GD目前仍然留醫。據軍方消息指，GD的腳踝並非服役期間受傷，入伍前已出現疼痛情況。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）"},{"pid":"8b15c9aca53e0e8531d74c5675c0e710e4b0e3f8","tid":695072,"uid":3818,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"女人真係多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad492e9604087ddffe03c60ca40cb1caece88a7a","tid":695072,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"唱歌跳舞又唔見你病唔見你入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62128635e91991cf6bbb1fd95fe27a2b7bae8e0","tid":695072,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b15c9aca53e0e8531d74c5675c0e710e4b0e3f8","tid":695072,"uid":3818,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"女人真係多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"Man 我只想做好自己"},{"pid":"d87ffe3dde0f7deacd7fc5b4200b6e54d37af1e4","tid":695072,"uid":3549,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」 <br />\n<br />\n同志龍6歲離開父母，開始了自己的演藝生涯。同志龍拍第一部片子《gay dragon 》系列電影時，他和300多人打打殺殺，因為太過入戲，他不小心踢到了廢鋼鐵，腳立即受傷，血如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n導演立刻喊停，要送他去醫院。他知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「星途」也許從此就斷了。於是，17歲的他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著腳，穿上鞋子繼續拍攝。換了四個膠袋，倒出四袋血，戲拍完時，他幾乎暈倒。 <br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。在給他縫針之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給他縫針時，同志龍就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一針一針地縫著。一個17歲的少年，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。他知道，哭是沒有用的。 <br />\n<br />\n最後一針，同志龍對醫生說：「我來縫！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，他也只有四天的生命了，所以，他願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，他要給自己縫一針。 <br />\n<br />\n從給自己縫針那一天開始，他知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，他一直努力，不停地得獎，終於成為rap說得最好的人"},{"pid":"eb75127db1c9b99028181e784132e86a1a3d1cb9","tid":695072,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"肛門受傷？"},{"pid":"6318380cb1175bc9d82a0b06a7319e8d3aec5c17","tid":695072,"uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"eb75127db1c9b99028181e784132e86a1a3d1cb9","tid":695072,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"肛門受傷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝！"},{"pid":"5913feda8dd41174f70132fa6147c6ea405c77cf","tid":695072,"uid":75426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"韓國TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe8edb30fe2136e95635d1b87208fe997ffd464","tid":695072,"uid":21598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"從來沒有想過太認真..."},{"pid":"2ceda430cf65d4fcb3a61e64fa82954df7eb25f6","tid":695072,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe8edb30fe2136e95635d1b87208fe997ffd464","tid":695072,"uid":21598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"從來沒有想過太認真..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:19:55.000Z","msg":"I just wanna have some fun"},{"pid":"63386cd05f7681a23f70e591efaf173a90763a34","tid":695072,"uid":1790,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:05:21.000Z","msg":"用TL呢個稱號會唔會太抬舉呢件泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終TL人氣地位接近神級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1931950a1b1e256dce1cd55c0f0ba2d4e3c4acc8","tid":695072,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:05:24.000Z","msg":"Party with GD~~~"},{"pid":"758258c53f48abed30e79a9ec48aeaf2706361eb","tid":695072,"uid":73200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T22:23:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4105258cd69e195132b15861f226f849a458f5ca","tid":695072,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeae3a92e08d97840bcf4ade239a015045622f2a","tid":695072,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c9a39a26d248903df140f5d8d45af7aafdc7392","tid":695072,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"係咪男人黎架"},{"pid":"17c5a33cd053eb0a55aa0e732913293531be7286","tid":695072,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeae3a92e08d97840bcf4ade239a015045622f2a","tid":695072,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"應該係跟住TL個樣黎整"},{"pid":"64033f36ed82628b9502381205f6948532bc9301","tid":695072,"uid":186608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cfa99866a7272ac2b7180edda133b47bc30eee","tid":695072,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"想借啲意退役咋話"}]}